  "detailed_description": "<strong>Psychological horror \"Hazing - Night Shift\"</strong> tells the short and very creepy story of a police officer named Stanley. It was his first night on duty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A very alarming call was received to the rescue service. The woman cried hysterically and called for help. Then her voice stopped. There were beeps on the phone.</h2><br>Everything you will see in this game is real events from the scene. Are you brave enough to watch this film to the end?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Features:<br>1. Found-footage horror.<br>2. VHS filter immerses you in the atmosphere even more<br>3. Realistic graphics<br>4. Very scary sounds<br>5. No artificial screamers. Only what can scare you in reality.<br>6. A short horror story that will stay in your memory forever.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is a game with a very depressing and dark atmosphere. The action will take place in a country house in which something very bad happened. The player will encounter terrifying and inexplicable events through the eyes of an ordinary police officer. Every step of the hero will be filled with fear and sticky horror, because around you there is only night and darkness, and in this darkness something terrible and very hungry is hidden...<br><br>You will have to explore every corner of this gloomy house to understand who called you and why and why it is so quiet here now.<br><br>Solve terrible puzzles, interact with various objects and immerse yourself in the dark story of the game.<br><br>Average time to complete the game is 30 minutes",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Psychological horror \"Hazing - Night Shift\"</strong> tells the short and very creepy story of a police officer named Stanley. It was his first night on duty.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/3bca0bec1ac764b592fc7a3917c24f74.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A very alarming call was received to the rescue service. The woman cried hysterically and called for help. Then her voice stopped. There were beeps on the phone.</h2><br>Everything you will see in this game is real events from the scene. Are you brave enough to watch this film to the end?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/150eac175cca6d55bf5a7fbe7f296016.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Game Features:<br>1. Found-footage horror.<br>2. VHS filter immerses you in the atmosphere even more<br>3. Realistic graphics<br>4. Very scary sounds<br>5. No artificial screamers. Only what can scare you in reality.<br>6. A short horror story that will stay in your memory forever.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.poster.avif?t=1720952488\" width=690 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.webm?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2968170/extras/80e7222c4777ac1721e53568f3ecc610.mp4?t=1720952488\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>This is a game with a very depressing and dark atmosphere. The action will take place in a country house in which something very bad happened. The player will encounter terrifying and inexplicable events through the eyes of an ordinary police officer. Every step of the hero will be filled with fear and sticky horror, because around you there is only night and darkness, and in this darkness something terrible and very hungry is hidden...<br><br>You will have to explore every corner of this gloomy house to understand who called you and why and why it is so quiet here now.<br><br>Solve terrible puzzles, interact with various objects and immerse yourself in the dark story of the game.<br><br>Average time to complete the game is 30 minutes",
